javascript :  

   javascript is a scripting langguage .
   javascript works with browser 

writing js in HTML 

<script>    code is here    </script>

writing javascript in HTML we can fallow two diffrent ways 

1. internal javascript
2. external javascript 

1. internal javascript : document specified 

<script >  code   </script>

2. external javascript : application specific 

  sublimetext-> file-> new file->save as ->  file.js 
   write  js code 

   .js extension is mandatory

  external js access in html :  
  <script src="file.js"> </script>

  print functionality :

  document.write("hello javascript")

  document is html in javascript 
  write is a predefined keyword for printing 
  javascript is casesensitive    






